        <span style="font-family: 'Bauhaus 93'; font-weight: lighter; font-size: 22px; margin-right: 5px;">res</span>
        <span style="text-align: center; font-weight: 700; color: #888888; font-size: 26px; text-shadow: 1px 1px #000000;">Advantage</span>
